{"tid":1398744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫幫被捕義士 義士唔係condom","createTime":"2019-08-03T02:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T02:58:24.000Z","uid":34095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b75d4625237f60f9952b6db12655804aee218327","tid":1398744,"uid":34095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:31:07.000Z","msg":"我知道大家都好想幫被捕義士 好想為佢哋出返啖氣 俾佢地知道好多人企係佢果邊支持佢哋！但如果我地太激烈反擊對家嘅post/指控 只會引起對家動員更多人去抹黑 我相信呢個互相攻擊的局面唔係大家想見到嘅結果 所有義士行出嚟都係爭取香港成為一個更好的地方 所以我地一定要堅守<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span> <br />\n對義士不實指控同攻擊要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">report或者冷處理</span> 唔好等佢再發酵落去 最後所有1xx個被捕義士絕對唔係condom 大家一定要守護佢哋 無論法庭聲援﹑捐錢等都絕對要做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 齊上齊落！</span>"},{"pid":"bf645bec6b6841a6e372161c9f805a28bb38446f","tid":1398744,"uid":34095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"大家今日旺角見！"},{"pid":"3f11194e096942a1e24f138853eb913c427c5d90","tid":1398744,"uid":34095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:32:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"f1eef9ad154b5a670994fac8c7e3a25ab99bfbad","tid":1398744,"uid":34095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:56:24.000Z","msg":"大家要幫幫義士"},{"pid":"1d6818eaefc9264f8050b9550c2eac3d72ca0d49","tid":1398744,"uid":34095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"唔可以放棄任何一個"},{"pid":"bd6e2b21f88a4ece51dac371b30893045cc36d04","tid":1398744,"uid":34095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:57:03.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"dfc406d91c66016af104ecf41b84907a63e23463","tid":1398744,"uid":34095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:58:24.000Z","msg":"撤消控告被捕人士"}]}